      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SILENT ACCORD (1) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when third (19.97) at Goulburn in a Grade 5. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. CAMBRIDGE KING (3) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Missed the frame latest (21.70) when sixth over 365m at Nowra in a Grade 5. Suited here and expected to run well. VILIAME (6) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 2.5 lengths into second (17.78) at this track in a Mix 1/2/3 over 324m. Expected to feature again. FUMBLES (7) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (17.82) in a Grade 5 at this track last time out.",
